 | 創建= (trad.) {{ill|lt=Heian period|Q193292|WD=Q193292|1=Heian period}} ({{ill|lt=801|Q30008|WD=Q30008|1=801}}-{{ill|lt=900|Q23460|WD=Q23460|1=900}})
